      "四龙套|龙套甲": 1,
      "皇甫讷|米南适": 1,
      "皇甫讷|龙套甲": 1,
      "米南适|龙套甲": 1
    }
  },
  "scenes": [
    {
      "scene_index": 1,
      "label": "第一场",
      "characters_present": [
        "万物静观皆自得",
        "东皋公",
        "伍员",
        "我的父谏奏反把命送",
        "童儿"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（东皋公上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "门外青山绿水，黄花百草风吹。"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "昔年周游列国，习就满腹才学。如今看破世事，隐居山林安乐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老汉东皋公，曾拜扁鹊先生门下为徒。是我周游列国，看破世事，隐居山林，\n倒也逍遥自在。我有一好友，名唤皇甫讷，我二人情义相投，时常一处饮酒弹\n琴。这几日是他未到庄中前来，也不知为了何事。看今日天气晴和，不免去到\n山前山后，游玩一番便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "闲来无事步从容，\n东窗不觉日映红。\n四季看花与人同。"
        },
        {
          "character": "万物静观皆自得、伍员",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（伍员上。撞金钟。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "伍员马上怒气冲，\n逃出龙潭虎穴中。"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，伍员。可恨平王无道，害我满门。幸喜逃出樊城，要到吴国借兵报仇。行\n至此间，四面俱是高山峻岭，不知哪条道路，可通吴国？"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗯哼！"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那厢有一老丈，下马问来。\n啊，老丈请了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那旁来的敢是伍子胥？"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个？老丈！俺不是伍子胥，老丈不要认差了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我乃山中隐士，将军但讲何妨？"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺便是伍子胥，老丈何以知晓？"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那日老汉路过昭关，见挂有画图，与将军面貌相似，故而冒叫一声，将军莫怪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，将军，今欲何往？"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我有满腹含冤，要到吴国借兵报仇！行至此间，四面俱是高山峻岭。请问老丈，\n哪条道路可通吴国？"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军你来看，四面俱是高山峻岭，若要去到吴国，必须打从昭关经过。"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可有别路？"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呃，并无别路。"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不好了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（撞金钟。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "听说吴国路不通，\n好似狼牙箭穿胸！"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "哭头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "心猿意马终何用！\n爹娘啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（撞金钟。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "血海冤仇落了空。"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军不必如此，此处离寒舍不远，请到寒舍一叙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "萍水相逢，怎好打搅？"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四海之内皆是朋友。请呐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "山在西来水在东，\n山水无处不想逢。\n人到何处不相逢！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（童儿上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "童儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "迎接家爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马匹带过。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（童儿拉马下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请问老丈尊姓大名？"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老汉东皋公。曾拜扁鹊先生门下为徒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，原来是前辈的老先生，失敬了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢。将军为何这等模样？"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唉，老丈啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "西皮快原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "恨平无无道乱楚宫，\n父纳子妻理难容！\n满门家眷血染红。"
        },
        {
          "character": "我的父谏奏反把命送、东皋公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来如此。啊，将军，老汉这里有一后花园，请将军暂住几日，待我想条妙计，\n救你出关就是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "若得如此，感恩非浅。"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军请。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忠臣孝子当维护，"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "愧煞男儿不丈夫！"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军是大丈夫！"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "惭愧！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（东皋公、伍员同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "伍员→东皋公",
