    },
    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "东皋公",
        "伍员",
        "童儿"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（伍员上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "过了一天又一天，\n心中好似滚油煎。\n不能报却父母冤！"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "幸遇东皋公，将我隐藏后花园中，一连几日，并无动静。今日又是一天，好不\n愁闷人也。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖起初更鼓〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唉，爹娘啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "一轮明月照窗前，\n愁人心中似箭穿。\n又谁知昭关又有阻拦。\n他将我隐藏在后花园。\n夜夜何曾得安眠。\n满腹含冤我向谁言；\n我好比龙游在浅沙滩；\n我好比波浪中失舵的舟船。\n今夜晚怎能够盼到明天。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖起二更鼓〗。东皋公上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "夤夜漏声催晓箭，\n月移花影上栏杆。\n且听愁人口内言。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖起三更鼓〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "心中有事难合眼，\n翻来覆去睡不安。\n叫人难解巧机关。\n为何几日他不言？\n你就该拿我献与昭关。\n哭一声爹娘不能相见，不能见！\n爹娘呀！\n要相逢除非是梦里团圆。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖起四更鼓〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "听他言来心好惨，\n铁石人儿也泪涟。\n想条妙计救他出关。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（东皋公下。〖起五更鼓〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "鸡鸣犬吠五更天，\n越思越想越伤惨。\n朝臣待漏五更寒。\n我冷冷清清向谁言！\n我本当拔宝剑自寻短见，寻短见！\n爹娘啊！\n父母冤仇化尘烟。\n我不杀平王我的心怎甘。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（东皋公上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "鸡鸣五鼓星斗散，\n将军开门有话言。"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "开门来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "二黄导板",
          "musical_style": "二黄导板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "适才朦胧将合眼！"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "开门来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "二黄散板",
          "musical_style": "二黄散板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "忽听门外有人言。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（伍员开门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "二黄散板",
          "musical_style": "二黄散板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "将军为何白了髯？"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，将军，一夜之间为何须发皓然了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我却不信。"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你自己看来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "二黄散板",
          "musical_style": "二黄散板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "冤仇未报容颜变，\n一事无成两鬓斑。"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恭喜将军，贺喜将军！"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喜从何来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军可以过得昭关了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎见得？"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我有一好友，名唤皇甫讷。待我请他前来，想条妙计救你出关就是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但凭老丈。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（童儿暗上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "童儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "拿我名帖，请皇甫官人，过庄一叙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "童儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老丈请上，受我一拜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也有一拜！"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "但愿过的昭关险，\n满斗焚香谢苍天。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（东皋公、伍员同下。）"
