          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（东皋公上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "袖内机关安排定，\n特到昭关走一程。"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此已是。\n门上哪位在？"
        },
        {
          "character": "龙套甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "做什么的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "烦劳通禀：东皋公求见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "龙套甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "候着。\n启禀大将军：东皋公求见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "米南适",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦？皋公兄到了？说我出迎。\n皋公兄！"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大将军。恭喜将军，贺喜将军。"
        },
        {
          "character": "米南适",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喜从何来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闻得将军拿住伍子胥，我是特来贺喜呀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "米南适",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唉，再休提起，是他言道，他不是伍子胥，他叫什么皇甫讷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "皇甫讷？"
        },
        {
          "character": "米南适",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "乃是我的朋友。今在何处？"
        },
        {
          "character": "米南适",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呃，现在外面。"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我看来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "皇甫讷",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唉，你要救我一救啊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀。果然是我的朋友，快将他放了下来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "米南适",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，哦，快快放下来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四龙套",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "皇甫讷",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈！你们竟敢错拿好人，来来来，我与你面见平王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呃，看在我的面上，请回去吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "皇甫讷",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哼！若不看在皋公兄的份上，定不与你甘休！"
        },
        {
          "character": "米南适",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，是是是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "皇甫讷",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂有此理，这还了得！"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请回去吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（皇甫讷下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军这里来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "米南适",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "做什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "东皋公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "从今以后，把守昭关，需要小心，且莫叫那真正的伍子胥他就糊里糊涂的混出\n了昭关呐，哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "米南适",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是是是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（东皋公下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "米南适",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将官！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四龙套",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有！"
        },
        {
          "character": "米南适",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小心防守呃！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四龙套",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！"
        },
